; draws a simple 6-pointed star

to star :size
	repeat 6 [
		forward :size
		right 120
		forward :size
		left 60
	]
end

setPenSize 5
star 100


; Above shows you how to draw a 6-pointed star
; using simple commands.
; The regularStar command is internally more complex
; but using it can lead to drawing more sophisticated
; drawings with less code.
; A similar 6-pointed star can also be drawn with:
; regularStar 200 6